articles.title: About this site
articles.description: This site is set up by the PSI Visualization special interest group.
articles.contents:
If you are interested in our PSI VIS SIG, you can find out more here.
We are hosting the Wonderful Wednesday Meetings where we discuss interesting visualization once a month. They are free. Find out more information and sing up here.

articles.title: PSI Scientific Meeting
articles.description: This Webpage is set up to provide you with the material used in the PSI Scientific Meeting: Generating Insights through Modern Applications of Data Visualisation.
